ffect behavior - it affects digestion.</p><p>Without support from yeast and beneficial bacteria, stressed birds may struggle to:</p></span></div><div data-rid="e4fe373b-36d2-41f8-8079-f9f74a69d4be" class="r-17itolj"><div data-rid="f743144d-6dcf-433c-b395-43e4ea4100ca" class="r-1h7tw62"><div data-rid="bf2d0983-5f43-4f58-ad15-9e66198f445d" class="r-dqnb25"><div data-rid="525e9e81-005f-4932-a701-c8ece6103173" class="r-y0edo3"><picture data-rid="c64a4e67-139f-478b-8c12-841360c4c0b6" class="r-1m4zuao"><img src="https://images.replocdn.com/images/e9c38b45-365a-49ae-87d0-5160b2c9afec/9c8f19eb-d8ff-4f06-956c-f2a18692645e" class="r-1avc63g" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div><div data-rid="836d7678-017a-461b-80a4-8e694f751619" class="r-1x1wjai alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Break down feed efficiently</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="bc11c04e-c7a4-4b89-a832-7168c221391d" class="r-pc9ce4"><div data-rid="b10c00e9-f81d-47e8-bc23-4831dd81dbc7" class="r-1hq61n3"><div data-rid="b66e09c1-b81f-4f4e-9a2c-e666a6c9f01c" class="r-ogxj34"><picture data-rid="f330bcbf-9472-477d-b2c3-cd31ba9a85bc" class="r-s3caxa"><img src="https://images.replocdn.com/images/e9c38b45-365a-49ae-87d0-5160b2c9afec/0cadfd8e-609c-468e-8e39-6b4deafc42f6" class="r-jo43c" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div><div data-rid="98c33ebe-741b-42d0-a5ea-c52219cd760e" class="r-1spf2l0 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Absorb key nutrients</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="9b218625-c688-4c26-a545-c93bed619f0d" class="r-l8qrlc"><div data-rid="ece1e603-599a-4c5d-965e-473f2ab88100" class="r-1qvoexx"><div data-rid="33189d91-ba09-4e63-8717-973acfe2e0e7" class="r-1x2v25"><picture data-rid="fe3ea2c5-4c88-44ea-9e68-72d4ba6c4972" class="r-12d8yp4"><img src="https://images.replocdn.com/images/e9c38b45-365a-49ae-87d0-5160b2c9afec/d9157985-f790-44a7-b9cb-07545c5683fb" class="r-se7hk6" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div><div data-rid="8672e37e-dfbc-40c0-a943-c895f22e37da" class="r-6exkys alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Maintain normal digestive balance</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="ae89d60b-c991-4f22-a585-d6bd555c2013" class="r-1bp9ds0 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>That means birds can be eating the same feed - but getting less out of it.</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="dcd8ec5c-9f99-492c-bb0b-14cf3d408546" class="r-dw9jub"><div data-rid="6b8d1166-ef27-46fc-a9f8-33aa0be4eded" class="r-iw5pi5"><div data-rid="ec2bd5d8-3573-49f2-93bb-9c60e547ceb5" class="r-hoy4wd alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h3>4. Heat, Cold, and Oxidative Stress Push Birds Toward Their Limits</h3></span></div><div data-rid="aa6439f7-4480-41b3-bb44-83eff26d4d8f" class="r-1yyfa3j alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Extreme temperatures and seasonal changes place real strain on a bird’s system.</p><p>Without consistent vitamin, mineral, and betaine support, stress compounds day after day increasing the risk of <strong>serious complications</strong> across the flock.</p><p>This is why problems often appear suddenly, even though stress has been building quietly.</p></span></div><div data-rid="bb47fe86-b8ff-4cf4-b1aa-69de28cb967d" class="r-1sirjs0"><picture data-rid="c48677f7-c5c3-4a9d-9af2-e58e03437e9d" class="r-1a87hrb"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/fdd5614c-e48f-4183-abe2-06ecde4315b2/1ff0ba2c-c1e7-4cc5-b20c-45ca2e9c268a?width=120" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/fdd5614c-e48f-4183-abe2-06ecde4315b2/1ff0ba2c-c1e7-4cc5-b20c-45ca2e9c268a?width=180" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/fdd5614c-e48f-4183-abe2-06ecde4315b2/1ff0ba2c-c1e7-4cc5-b20c-45ca2e9c268a?width=180" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/fdd5614c-e48f-4183-abe2-06ecde4315b2/1ff0ba2c-c1e7-4cc5-b20c-45ca2e9c268a" class="r-egqgkv" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="4e173265-4b